messages.message: <!here> need some help with Process file settings related to correct orientation. Please let me know if anyone is free. Easier to explain the problem over a call

I don't know if docs will help, but here's the link to the Process File step configuration https://www.instabase.com/docs/reference/apps/flow/step-config-reference/process-files/

lmk if docs need updates, if you have a question perhaps other users do too.

Hi Barrie. Thanks for that. But this one's not related to the docs. Its how the page height and width turns up when the flag "correct orientation" is set tot true. Just wanted to understand what happens under the hood which would possibly help me solve my problem
Guess I figured it out for now. thank you :slightly_smiling_face:

in case you dont know, you can always record bugs/issues using loom and share the video https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/loom-for-chrome/liecbddmkiiihnedobmlmillhodjkdmb?hl=en-US
Its pretty easy to use
